  "body": "Hi,\r\n\r\nWhen the Eth1 node is restarted, the beacon node starts reporting failed websocket connections without trying to re-establish them:\r\n```\r\n*powchain.Service: ERROR websocket: close 1006 (abnormal closure): unexpected EOF\r\ntime=\"2019-11-19 18:27:03\" level=warning msg=\"Node is unhealthy!\" prefix=prometheus statuses=\"*powchain.Service: ERROR websocket: close 1006 (abnormal closure): unexpected EOF\r\n```\r\nThe beacon node should try to re-establish the connection to the Eth1 chain.",
